SUMMARY: Macrame & Mixology Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Let's knot miss this one!\n\nNew Projects Every Month!\n\n**M
 ixology & Macramé Workshop**\n\n*Beginner Friendly – Kid Friendly – Socia
 l Craft Experience w/ Katherine Bergin\n\n*Join us for a creative and rel
 axing afternoon at our Mixology & Macramé Workshop! Learn to craft differ
 ent macramé pieces of your own while enjoying a drink in our cozy Barrel 
 Room @ Griffo Distillery. This is the perfect opportunity to unwind\, con
 nect\, and take home a handmade creation! See you Saturdays!\n\n**What's 
 Happening: Mixology & Macramé Workshop\n\n**Where: Griffo Distillery Tast
 ing Bar\n\n**When: 2nd Saturdays of Every Month - 2:30-4:30 PM\n\n**Works
 hop Highlights:**\nLearn step-by-step how to craft a beautiful macramé pi
 ece to take home. All materials will be provided\, so just bring your cre
 ativity!\n\n*Past projects include: Plant hangers\, wall hangings\, coast
 ers\, and more!\n\n**Relaxing Atmosphere:** Enjoy specialty cocktails cra
 fted with Griffo's award-winning spirits while you create.\n\n**Kid-Frien
 dly Fun:** This workshop is beginner-friendly and open to all ages\, maki
 ng it a great activity for families\, friends\, or solo attendees.\n\n**C
 ost of Admission:**\n\n- $40 – Pay upon Arrival\n\nSpace is limited\, so 
 RSVP early to ensure your spot at the table.\n\n
