SUMMARY: Saturday Acoustic with David Correa at Adobe Road Winery
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Ado
 be Road Winery in Downtown Petaluma https://adoberoadwines.com/visit/ . S
 ip on award-winning wines while enjoying talented local musicians in a wa
 rm and inviting atmosphere. Choose from wines by the glass or bottle to d
 iscover new favorites. Reserve your spot on Tock https://www.exploretock.
 com/adoberoadwines/ and make it a memorable night of great music\, fine w
 ine\, and good company!\n\nDavid Correa is a celebrated guitarist and com
 poser blending Latin rhythms with Spanish and world music influences. Sin
 ce 1999\, The David Correa Group has built a loyal fanbase across the Bay
  Area and beyond with energetic\, rhythm-driven performances. The group h
 as toured extensively throughout the western U.S. and earned multiple acc
 olades\, including three consecutive NORBAY Awards for Best Latin Band. C
 orrea has released seven albums\, including New Moon and Alta Vista\, and
  has been featured alongside New Flamenco greats like Ottmar Liebert and 
 Jesse Cook. His live shows promise a vibrant mix of soulful guitar\, rhyt
 hm\, and musical storytelling.
CATEGORIES:music,live-music,winery,wine
