  for ASL Social Hours\, a welcoming space to practice American Sign Langua
 ge (ASL)\, connect with others\, and build community in a relaxed\, suppor
 tive environment. Whether you're brand new to ASL or already signing\, eve
 ryone is welcome to drop in\, learn\, and have fun together!</p><p>  Monda
 ys: 3:30 PM – 4:30 PM<br />  Wednesdays: 1:30 PM – 2:30 PM</p><p>  Com
 e by\, meet new people\, and sign in a friendly social setting! The DCC is
  on the 3rd floor landing of the Bertolini Student Center.</p><p>  For any
  questions or access needs\, please email <a href="mailto:srjcdcc@santaros
 a.edu">srjcdcc@santarosa.edu</a>&#160\;</p><p>  Visit the <a href="https:/
