 RJC Student Activities Center (SAC)  Free parking is available in the Mend
 ocino Avenue lot behind My Friend Joe Coffee. No parking tickets will be i
 ssued in this lot during the event.  All are welcome to stop by\, view the
  artwork and enjoy some food and light refreshments.
