SUMMARY:Joose @ Vintage Space ( Flamingo SR)  🍺🎸🎛
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nDon’t miss JOOSE at Vintage Space\, 
 Flamingo Santa Rosa\, April 18th! High-energy '90s rock hits from Nirvana\
 , Sublime\, Metallica & more!\n\nOn Saturday\, April 18th\, Vintage Space 
 at The Flamingo transforms into a high-octane rock haven as JOOSE\, Santa 
 Rosa's own legendary '90s rock cover band\, takes the stage!\n\nWhy You Ca
 n't Miss This: JOOSE is more than a band—they’re a full-throttle nosta
 lgia machine\, delivering electrifying renditions of rock anthems from Nir
 vana\, Green Day\, Sublime\, Metallica\, and more! With a setlist that fee
 ls like the ultimate mixtape of your favorite '90s rock hits\, JOOSE has b
 een packing North Bay venues with their high-energy performances and unmat
 ched vibes.\n\nWho’s in JOOSE?\nFronted by the powerhouse vocals of Jame
 s Erickson and backed by the thunderous rhythm section of Scott Essig\, Mi
 tch Nunley\, and Dan Sartin\, JOOSE brings every note and riff to life wit
 h pure passion and precision.\n\nThe Venue:Vintage Space at The Flamingo i
 s the ultimate spot for an unforgettable night. Its retro-modern vibe and 
 intimate setting make it the perfect backdrop for JOOSE’s explosive perf
 ormance.\n\nGrab your tickets early—this WILL sell out!\n\nHit the bar f
 or craft cocktails\, and fuel up with bites before the show.\n\nBring your
  crew and your loudest singing voice—this is the night to rock out!\n\nW
 HEN: Saturday\, April 18th\n\nWHERE: Vintage Space @ The Flamingo\, Santa 
 Rosa\n\nTIME: Doors open at 8 PM | Show starts at 9 PM\n\nDon’t just hea
 r the music—FEEL IT. JOOSE is ready to bring the house down. Are you rea
 dy to party like it’s 1995!\n\nTickets - $20
