SUMMARY:Redwood Empire Whiskey Tasting
DESCRIPTION:Redwood Empire Whiskey Tasting Night \n\n\n\nMcNear’s • Red Bull Room • Wilibees Wine & Spirits Petaluma \n\n\n\nTuesday\, April 21\, 2026 \n\n\n\nEvent 5:30 PM / Doors 5pm \n\n\n\nJoin us for a special Redwood Empire Whiskey Tasting Night in the Red Bull Room at McNear’s on Tuesday\, April 21 at 5:30pm. Explore an incredible lineup of bold bourbons\, ryes\, blends\, and limited cask-strength pours from one of California’s most celebrated whiskey houses. \n\n\n\nTasting led by Master Blender Lauren Patz. \n\n\n\nWhether you’re a seasoned whiskey lover or just looking for a fun and flavorful night out\, this is a rare chance to taste your way through an exceptional range of Redwood Empire expressions. Redwood Empire’s lineup includes fan favorites like Emerald Giant Rye and Lost Monarch Blend alongside special releases like Rocket Top\, Grizzly Beast\, Foggy Burl\, and Haystack Needle. \n\n\n\nChef curated bites paired with each whiskey tasting. \n\n\n\nVery limited seating. This event sells out frequently. \n\n\n\n$75 per person – includes tax and tip. Grab tickets at McNear’s bar to avoid online service fees. \n\n\n\nTasting led by Master Blender Lauren Patz. \n\n\n\nFeatured tasting lineup: \n\n\n\n\nPipedream Bourbon \n\n\n\nEmerald Giant Rye\n\n\n\nLost Monarch American Whiskey \n\n\n\nGrizzly Beast Bottled in Bond Bourbon \n\n\n\nRocket Top Bottled in Bond Rye\n\n\n\n\nFood Menu: \n\n\n\n1st Course – Pipedream Bourbon \n\n\n\nPork Belly Confit- Coconut corn puree\, apple chutney\, maple + chili glaze \n\n\n\n2nd Course- Emerald Giant Rye \n\n\n\nTea smoked beets\, baby greens\, Chandler strawberries\, whipped Bay Blue cheese\, pickled onion\, pistachio\, golden balsamic vinaigrette \n\n\n\n3rd Course – Lost Monarch \n\n\n\nHalibut Crudo- Citrus cured halibut\, sugar snap peas\, grapefruit\, basil\, chili crunch \n\n\n\n4th Course- Grizzle Beast \n\n\n\nDurham Ranch Bison Ribeye \n\n\n\nGreen garlic mashed potatoes\, Delta asparagus\, spring onions\, Grizzle Beast demi\, roasted bone marrow butter \n\n\n\n5th Course -Rocket Top \n\n\n\nTres Leches-Blueberry compote\, brown butter maple crumble\, vanilla bean cake. \n\n\n\nVery limited seating. This event sells out frequently. \n\n\n\n$75 per person – includes tax and tip. Grab tickets at McNear’s bar to avoid online service fees.
URL:https://www.mcnears.com/event/redwood-empire-whiskey-tasting/
END:VEVENT
