DESCRIPTION:The Petaluma Cinema Series is a film education program that br
 ings together SRJC film students\, the campus community\, and Sonoma Count
 y residents to engage in dialogue around classic\, foreign\, &amp\; indepe
 ndent films. Presentations feature SRJC film faculty\, industry guests\, i
 nterdisciplinary experts\, and technical demonstrations. All evenings incl
 ude post-screening discussions.Pre-film program: 6pm  Film screening: 7pm 
 (longer run times begin at 6:30pm)  Post-screening discussion until 10pm  
   For more information\, visit: https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-se
 ries/ (https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-series/)&#160\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T003504Z
