SUMMARY:Food For Thought’s Plant Sale & Garden Tour
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260425T120000
UID:1da74e79b359a19c0dfbb54f9768cca3@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Guided tours of the garden and food bank available by request.
  Support a great cause while celebrating the joy of gardening! This annual
  plant sale fundraiser is hosted by Food For Thought food bank\, helping p
 rovide healthy food and compassionate support to those in need. Explore th
 e thriving Food For Thought garden\, get inspired by what’s growing for 
 the food bank\, and shop a variety of veggie\, herb\, and flower starts to
  bring home—lovingly grown by Food For Thought volunteers and community 
 partners. Every purchase helps feed our neighbors in need. Since 1988\, Fo
 od for Thought has provided life-sustaining groceries\, meals\, and loving
  support to people living with serious medical conditions in Sonoma County
 —all free of charge. For more information\, visit fftfoodbank.org/plant-
 sale
LOCATION:Petaluma\, CA
URL:https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/food-for-thought-s-
 plant-sale-garden-tour
