SUMMARY:16th Annual Spring Plant Sale
DESCRIPTION:Come get sustainably grown vegetable\, herb\, and flower starts
  for your spring/summer garden. We accept cash\, card\, and CalFresh/EBT. 
 We offer a 50% discount for CalFresh/EBT customers up to $20.\n\nLocation:
  Petaluma Bounty Community Farm at 55 Shasta Ave.\, Petaluma\n\nThis sale 
 is open to all from 10 a.m. to 3 p.m. We will have a special shopping hour
  (9-10 a.m.) for immunocompromised customers\, people with disabilities\, 
 and CalFresh customers paying with their EBT cards.\nWe will post more inf
 ormation on our Plant Sale page as the date approaches. 
END:VEVENT
