DESCRIPTION:Join us for Disability Support Hour at the SRJC Disability Cul
 tural Center. This is a welcoming space for disabled students and allies t
 o connect\, share experiences\, ask questions\, and build community.&#160\
 ;  Whether you're looking for peer support\, conversation\, or just a plac
 e to be among others who understand\, you're invited to stop by and be par
 t of the DCC community.The DCC is on the third-floor landing in the Bertol
 ini Student Center.  For any additional access needs or questions\, please
  send us an email at srjcdcc@santarosa.edu (mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu)&
 #160\;  Visit the DRD website here! (https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc)
