CATEGORIES:Department Events
DESCRIPTION:The SRJC Fashion Studies Program is excited to present our ann
 ual Spring Fashion Show\, a celebration of the talent and creativity of ou
 r students.  This year's theme "The Equinox" is inspired by the moment whe
 n night and day stand in balance\, presenting fashion as a dialogue betwee
 n opposites\; structure and freedom\, rebellion and hope\, darkness and ra
 diant color.Doors open at 7pm and the runway show begins at 7:30pm.For mor
 e information and tickets\, visit the SRJC's Fashion Studies website! (htt
 ps://fashion.santarosa.edu/event/spring-2026-fashion-show)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T210400Z
LOCATION:Clocktower Plaza - SRJC Petaluma Campus
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/17430-2026-spring-fashion-show
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The SRJC Fashion Studies Program is exci
 ted to present our annual Spring Fashion Show\, a celebration of the talen
 t and creativity of our students.</p><p>  This year's theme "The Equinox" 
 is inspired by the moment when night and day stand in balance\, presenting
  fashion as a dialogue between opposites\; structure and freedom\, rebelli
 on and hope\, darkness and radiant color.</p><p><strong>Doors open at 7pm 
 and the runway show begins at 7:30pm.</strong></p><p><a href="https://fash
 ion.santarosa.edu/event/spring-2026-fashion-show" target="_blank" rel="noo
 pener">For more information and tickets\, visit the SRJC's Fashion Studies
  website!</a></p>
