X-SOURCE-ID:gcal_c_69dcaa6c13b06c1111a1706565ebb272c3d24290c650a9378bdbd37bff886879
X-SOURCE:Petaluma Community Center
DTSTART:20260501T210000Z
DTEND:20260502T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260411T025324Z
UID:6id3p3roiflefpj3o3lh78kebd@google.com
CREATED:20260225T153103Z
DESCRIPTION:<h2><strong>Sip\, Stroll &amp\; Stay Funky: The Petaluma Rallie
  Progressive Tasting</strong> 🍷🚐</h2><p>Park the trailer and grab your wa
 lking shoes! Immerse yourself in the soulful\, artistic heart of downtown P
 etaluma with an exclusive progressive wine path curated specifically for th
 e <strong>Vintage Camper Trailer Magazine's Petaluma Rallie</strong>.</p><p
 >Experience the <strong>historic charm</strong> of our river town—where Vic
 torian architecture meets a vibrant\, modern art scene—as you wander betwee
 n three of Petaluma's most celebrated\, award-winning tasting rooms. All th
 ree locations are situated within a short\, scenic stroll of one another.</
 p><hr /><h3><strong>The Award-Winning Lineup:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><stro
 ng><a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://www.brooksnote.com/" ta
 rget="_blank">Brooks Note Winery</a>:</strong> Industrial chic\, soulful\, 
 and family-owned\, focusing on the best of the Petaluma Gap.</p></li><li><p
 ><strong><a href="https://adoberoadwines.com/" target="_blank">Adobe Road W
 inery</a>:</strong> High-octane luxury and world-class craftsmanship in a s
 tunning waterfront setting.</p></li><li><p><strong><a href="https://www.rus
 sewines.com/" target="_blank">Montagne Russe Winery</a>:</strong> A funky\,
  small-batch urban winery and record lounge where art and wine collide.</p>
 </li></ul><hr /><h3><strong>The Details:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Wh
 en:</strong> Friday\, May 1 | 2\;00 PM – 5:00 PM</p></li><li><p><strong>Wha
 t:</strong> A curated flight of <strong>3 award-winning wines</strong> at <
 strong>each</strong> location (9 wines total!).</p></li><li><p><strong>Vibe
 :</strong> Uniquely Petaluma. Think industrial-chic galleries\, historic st
 orefronts\, and world-class cool-climate pours.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cost
 :</strong> <strong>$60 per person</strong> for the full three-winery circui
 t.</p></li></ul><p>Don't just visit Petaluma—taste the creative spirit that
  makes us the most inspired corner of wine country. Grab your rally mates a
 nd come celebrate the art of the pour!</p><p>Purchase Tickets <a href="http
 s://www.brooksnotewinery.com/product/vct-petaluma-rallie-progressive-wine-s
 troll">Here:</a>  </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T153345Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Vintage Camper Trailer Magazine - Petaluma Rallie Progressive Wine 
 Stroll
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
