SUMMARY:53rd Annual Bodega Bay Fisherman's Festival
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nThis is one of my **absolute favorite*
 * events of the year!! Join us in beautiful Bodega Bay for the 53rd Annual
  Fisherman's Festival! 🐟☀️🌊\nThis festival is on the small side 
 but very fun\, **dog friendly too!!** 🐕🐶and very Sonoma Coast vibes.
 \nThere will will be music 🎸🎵\, beer 🍻\, wine 🍷 and food truck
 s 🌯🦐🚚! Bonus: the headliner is **TAINTED LOVE!**\n\nThere are $18
  pre-sale tickets right now until April 24th. I think it's $25 after that 
 and at the event entrance. There is also an option to buy a 2-day pass for
  $30 right now (I will only be hosting for Saturday but will go Sunday too
  to see **Mustache Harbor!**.\n\nSee link below for more event info.\nI wi
 ll update the description soon if I can find shuttle info. See you there!!
  🌞\nBodega Bay Fisherman’s Festival - Bodega Bay Fisherman's Festival
  https://share.google/axl7RxOueTC2Y6yLQ
