CATEGORIES:Department Events
DESCRIPTION:Join the SRJC Disability Cultural Center for ASL Social Hours\
 , a welcoming space to practice American Sign Language (ASL)\, connect wit
 h others\, and build community in a relaxed\, supportive environment. Whet
 her you're brand new to ASL or already signing\, everyone is welcome to dr
 op in\, learn\, and have fun together!  Mondays: 3:30 PM – 4:30 PM  Wedn
 esdays: 1:30 PM – 2:30 PM  Come by\, meet new people\, and sign in a fri
 endly social setting! The DCC is on the 3rd floor landing of the Bertolini
  Student Center.  For any questions or access needs\, please email srjcdcc
 @santarosa.edu (mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu)&#160\;  Visit the DRD websit
 e here! (https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T210304Z
LOCATION:Bertolini Student Center\, 3rd floor\, DCC - Santa Rosa Campus
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/15604-dcc-asl-social-hour
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join the SRJC Disability Cultural Center
  for ASL Social Hours\, a welcoming space to practice American Sign Langua
 ge (ASL)\, connect with others\, and build community in a relaxed\, suppor
 tive environment. Whether you're brand new to ASL or already signing\, eve
 ryone is welcome to drop in\, learn\, and have fun together!</p><p>  Monda
 ys: 3:30 PM – 4:30 PM<br />  Wednesdays: 1:30 PM – 2:30 PM</p><p>  Com
 e by\, meet new people\, and sign in a friendly social setting! The DCC is
  on the 3rd floor landing of the Bertolini Student Center.</p><p>  For any
  questions or access needs\, please email <a href="mailto:srjcdcc@santaros
 a.edu">srjcdcc@santarosa.edu</a>&#160\;</p><p>  Visit the <a href="https:/
 /drd.santarosa.edu/dcc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DRD website here!</
 a></p>
