 s_collective_district_calendar_1.rev.1772228011.png
CATEGORIES:Department Events
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Disability Support Hour at the SRJC Disability Cul
 tural Center. This is a welcoming space for disabled students and allies t
 o connect\, share experiences\, ask questions\, and build community.&#160\
 ;  Whether you're looking for peer support\, conversation\, or just a plac
 e to be among others who understand\, you're invited to stop by and be par
 t of the DCC community.The DCC is on the third-floor landing in the Bertol
 ini Student Center.  For any additional access needs or questions\, please
  send us an email at srjcdcc@santarosa.edu (mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu)&
 #160\;  Visit the DRD website here! (https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T213429Z
LOCATION:Bertolini Student Center\, 3rd floor\, DCC - Santa Rosa Campus
URL:https://calendar.santarosa.edu/event/15556-disability-support-hour
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join us for Disability Support Hour at t
 he SRJC Disability Cultural Center. This is a welcoming space for disabled
  students and allies to connect\, share experiences\, ask questions\, and 
 build community.&#160\;</p><p>  Whether you're looking for peer support\, 
 conversation\, or just a place to be among others who understand\, you're 
 invited to stop by and be part of the DCC community.</p><p><strong>The DCC
  is on the third-floor landing in the Bertolini Student Center.</strong></
 p><p>  For any additional access needs or questions\, please send us an em
 ail at <a href="mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu">srjcdcc@santarosa.edu</a>&#1
 60\;</p><p>  Visit the <a href="https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc" target="_bl
 ank" rel="noopener">DRD website here!</a></p>
