 h others\, and build community in a relaxed\, supportive environment. Whet
 her you're brand new to ASL or already signing\, everyone is welcome to dr
 op in\, learn\, and have fun together!  Mondays: 3:30 PM – 4:30 PM  Wedn
 esdays: 1:30 PM – 2:30 PM  Come by\, meet new people\, and sign in a fri
 endly social setting! The DCC is on the 3rd floor landing of the Bertolini
  Student Center.  For any questions or access needs\, please email srjcdcc
 @santarosa.edu (mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu)&#160\;  Visit the DRD websit
 e here! (https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc)
