SUMMARY: Santa's Riverboat Arrival & Small Business Saturday
DESCRIPTION:Santa's Riverboat Arrival\n\nSaturday\, November 28\, 2026\n\
 n11:30am - 1:30pm at River Plaza Shopping Center\n\nSanta and Mrs. Claus 
 are coming to town on November 28\, the Saturday after Thanksgiving!\n\nW
 hen Santa arrives in Petaluma\, he leaves his sleigh at home. Instead\, h
 e and Mrs. Claus make a uniquely Petaluma arrival - they sail up the Peta
 luma River on a Lind Marine tugboat and dock at River Plaza Shopping Cent
 er on E. Washington to the cheers of excited children!\n\nStarting at 11:
 30 am\, families will enjoy live entertainment while waiting for Santa an
 d Mrs. Claus to arrive! The Christmas couple will arrive around noon and 
 will be welcomed by costumed dancers from the Petaluma School of Ballet’s
  “Nutcracker.” Santa and Mrs. Claus will make their way across the parkin
 g lot to their festive tent outside Taps Restaurant where they will be av
 ailable for family photos. Be sure to bring your Christmas wish list!\n\n
 Santa would love to spend all afternoon in Petaluma\, but in order to hea
 r from all the good boys and girls all over the world\, he will have to b
 e on his way to his next destination at 1:30 pm.\n\nDon’t let the fun sto
 p there! Keep the festive mood flowing by taking your Shop Small swag bag
  and make the short walk to historic downtown Petaluma to support local s
 hopping. When we all shop small\, it's not just for the things we love\, 
 but for the businesses we love\, for the community we call home\, and to 
 help promote local economic growth. Learn more about Small Business Satur
 day http://shopsmall.com/ and visit the official Small Business Saturday 
 Facebook https://www.facebook.com/shopsmall/ page. And take advance of sh
 op small benefits by using your American Express card by viewing this lin
 k here https://www.americanexpress.com/en-us/maps?country=US&near=Petalum
 a\,CA&cat=Shop-Small&cl=38.232417\,-122.6366524&intlink=us-GABM-Shop_Smal
 l_Map .\n\nVisit http://PetalumaDowntown.com for more information!
CATEGORIES:
X-TKF-FEATURED-IMAGE:https://d3flpus5evl89n.cloudfront.net/5e1e2fe9df82fe
 0e2d29328c/63ed2f540a1a82239ea65111/scaled_256.jpg
X-TKF-CUSTOM-PREVIEW:Santa's Riverboat Arrival Saturday\, November 28\, 2
 026 11:30am - 1:30pm at River Plaza Shopping Center Santa and Mrs. Claus 
 are coming to town on November...
LOCATION:River Plaza Shopping Center\,54 E Washington St\, Petaluma\, CA 
 94952\, USA
